markdownRemark.html: Samuel Roads, Jr. reproduces a receipt between Jonathan Dodge, Caffee's enslaver, and Edmund Gale of the Snow Diligence for the loan of Caffee for a voyage to Cape Fear, London, and then back to New England in 1742.
